@uri=http://localhost:2918



### Select one
GET {{uri}}/book/1 HTTP/1.1


### Select All - Limit 10
GET {{uri}}/books HTTP/1.1


### No paging, no search. listCount of /db/db.go: 3
POST {{uri}}/books HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Paging
POST {{uri}}/books HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "options": {
        "page": 0,
        "count": 3
    }
}


### Search
### keywords -> book{name and author and price ...} or book{name and author and price} ...
### book 내부는 and, book끼리는 or
POST {{uri}}/books HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "keywords": [
        {
            "author": "칼 세이건"
        },
        {
            "author": "김용"
        },
        {
            "name": "흔한남매 7",
            "author": "백난도"
        }
    ],
    "options": {
        "page": 0,
        "count": 3
    }
}

